ve">Darlene Love</a>也加入了雪儿五年来的首张专辑。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_91 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_91" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cher-announces-first-ever-christmas-album-and-shares-first-single-dj-play-a-christmas-song-3510567"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> Cher 的上一张长片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/cher-dancing-queen-review-abba-2383579">《Dancing Queen》</a>于 2018 年问世。 <em>NME</em>在四星评论中写道：“Cher 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">ABBA</a>翻唱专辑令人愉悦，同时也令人惊讶地心酸。”</p></div></div><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-hanks-is-a-big-fan-of-cher-in-mamma-mia-2-3553440">汤姆·汉克斯 (Tom Hanks) 是《妈妈咪呀 2》中雪儿 (Cher) 的忠实粉丝，这一</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
